<span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;color:#333340;background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow">By any measure, Trump is a really rich dude. But his fixation on ceaselessly tossing out sky-high figures displays a routine neediness that&#8217;s cause
