<span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;color:#333340">&#8220;A fellow asked me that once and I said, &#8216;I don&#8217;t know,&#8221; Nelson Bunker Hunt once told a congressional panel grilling&nbsp;him about his net worth. &#8220;But I do know people who know how much they
